Finding: F-005
Date: 2026-04-20
Figma node: I3235:5081;8485:38041
Property: icon size
Expected: 20×20 heroicons-mini/magnifying-glass
Actual: 16×16 custom svg
Severity: Medium
File: src/components/TopNav.tsx:27-30

Reasoning: Figma uses the 20×20 heroicons-mini magnifying-glass. Geometry
is scaled proportionally (cx/cy, r, path coords) so stroke weight reads
consistently at the new size.

